data.description: WHO NEEDS A DEEP WATER BOAT SLIP?CHANGE YOUR LATITUDE! A unit like this rarely comes on the market. 2 bedroom condo located directly on the Intercoastal with a deeded deep water boat slip. Short term rentals ok! Owner has freshened up the unit with new LV flooring, and fresh coat of paint.  Condo comes with 1 deeded parking space.  Plenty of overflow parking in guest spaces.  Kitchen is equipped with custom cabinetry with soft closing and duck tail drawers. Granite countertops in both the kitchen and bathroom. Out back you will find your very own deeded boat space, a private beach, a fish station, and a small boat ramp-the perfect place to launch a paddle board or small watercraft.  The private beach is the ultimate place to watch the sunset,  chill and grill while watching the dolphins play and the boat traffic pass through on their way to Destin, Navarre and beyond.  Both bedrooms have a water views with the master bedroom having a picturesque view of the Intercoastal.  Condo is a short walk to public beach access #1, plenty of bars and some of the best restaurants the Emerald Coast has to offer.  It's the best of both world- the Intercoastal and the beach!   Sellers have not rented this unit so you can start your short term rental empire with a clean slate.
